---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import kesikiImage from '../assets/images/kesiki.png';
import logoImage from '../assets/images/logo.png';
---

<section class="about section-shell" id="about" aria-labelledby="about-title">
  <div class="about__inner container">
    <div class="about__copy js-reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow__number">01</span><span class="eyebrow__label">ABOUT</span></p>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="about-title">今日の道のりを、<br /><span class="section-title__accent">明日の思い出へ。</span></h2>
      <p class="about__text">長野県佐久市、木々に囲まれた緑の家。バイクを降りてひと息ついたら、ここが今夜の居場所です。宿泊は素泊まり、またはキャンプから選べます。</p>
      <p class="about__note">バイク以外でも大丈夫。旅人なら自転車、車、徒歩どなたでも大歓迎です。</p>
      <div class="about__facts">
        <div class="about__fact"><span class="about__fact-value">10</span><span class="about__fact-unit">MIN.</span><span class="about__fact-label">布施温泉まで</span></div>
        <div class="about__fact"><span class="about__fact-value">30</span><span class="about__fact-unit">MIN.</span><span class="about__fact-label">佐久ICから車で</span></div>
        <div class="about__fact"><span class="about__fact-value">2</span><span class="about__fact-unit">ROOMS</span><span class="about__fact-label">客室数</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about__visual js-reveal">
      <div class="about__image-frame js-parallax-wrap">
        <Image
          class="about__image js-parallax"
          src={kesikiImage}
          alt="宿から望む佐久の田園と山並み"
          widths={[480, 720, 960, 1200]}
          sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 48vw"
          format="webp"
          quality={78}
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </div>
      <Image
        class="about__stamp"
        src={logoImage}
        alt=""
        width={380}
        height={380}
        format="webp"
        quality={85}
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <p class="about__caption">3841-337 Fuse, Saku</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
